title: Hitachi HNAS: Cluster Nodes
agents: hitachi_hnas_rest
catalog: hw/storagehw/hitachi
license: GPLv2
distribution: Kuhn & Rueß GmbH
description:
 This check monitors the cluster nodes of a Hitachi NAS (HNAS)
 system via the File Storage REST API. It requires the special
 agent "Hitachi HNAS via REST API" to be configured for the host.

 The service is OK if the node is ONLINE, otherwise it goes CRIT.
 In addition the model, firmware version and uptime of the node
 are reported.

item:
 The name of the cluster node.

discovery:
 One service is created for each cluster node.
